## ðŸ”§ Step 1: Create Custom Installer with Rufus

1. Download [Rufus](https://rufus.ie).
2. Download the Windows 11 ISO from [Microsoft](https://www.microsoft.com/software-download/windows11).
3. Insert a USB drive (at least 8GB).
4. Use Rufus to:
   - Select the ISO and USB drive.
   - Enable advanced options:
     - âœ… Bypass TPM, Secure Boot, and Microsoft Account requirements
     - âœ… Disable telemetry prompts during setup

